snippet.textDisplay:
nice...Very few people know that the first part of song "chand"i.e Sar sar per saadhar is very special and unique of its kind.Its RANNKI type and most diffcult. its breathless song .If u write this in hindi or gujarati there is no matra on upper side of word. It has very beautiful meaning and language is "Charni" not  exect gujarati. When Ravindranath tagor first heard this song from Kaag Bapu(famous gujarti poet ) he stand up and said "vahh..vahh" and he ask Kaag bapu that he want to meet the poet. kag bapu replied that this chand is more than 250 year old and till now no one is able to prepare song like this.

This chand was prepared by "Bhramanand swami" of swaminarayan sect.he was "sighra kavi" means he can prepare song spontaneously and this is example of his creativity.he has prepared more than 10,000 songs many of them are not available today.
I like the remix and they have mixed song of Narhasi mehta and bhramanand swami.
Enjoy......
